Class EditAddressActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • InputStepsActivity
      • com.adidas.connect.ui.activities.EditAddressActivity

  • public class EditAddressActivity
extends InputStepsActivity
    Activity to edit and delete an address. To check the result use the flag bits check or isChanged(int), isPrimaryChanged(int), isDeleted(int) methods.
